{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fc983b27cf","title":"致彭德怀等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"795dc1f369","index":0,"year":1936,"month":5,"day":28,"articleId":"fc983b27cf"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji8.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji8":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e9b7c8d3a9","type":"paragraph","text":"致彭德怀等电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"fc983b27cf"},{"id":"2f627ea0ac","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年5月28日）你们取得宁条梁后，将进到蒙民集中地区，要特别注意执行中央对内蒙人民的宣传，扶助蒙民自决，而不是赤化，以建立北线上的缓冲地带。当占领教堂区域时，如仔得神父，应特别优待，不应悔导。宣布凡属以前教堂及军阀所占领的蒙地，完全退还内蒙民众。[1]这是毛泽东和周恩来致红军第一方西军司令员、西方野战军司令员兼政治委员彭德怀、西方野战军政治部主任刘晓，红军第一方面军第十五军团军团长徐海东、政治委员程子华、政治部主任王首道电的主要内容。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"fc983b27cf"}],"page":{"id":"bcd57302d6","publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"fc983b27cf","start":433,"end":433}}}},"__N_SSG":true}